comments.body: After a successful year, Mr. Roo is goin to his well earned summer vocation. As he is not a fan of boring activities and always on the lookout for an adrenaline rush he decides to surf. Since I'm lucky as always, I was able to spot him in the waves and made this oil painting:Go Big Or Go HomeOil on canvasAfter his day full of sport and adrenaline he decides to go to a beach bar and enjoy the sunset while looking fabulous as always:La Dolce VitaOil on canvasHere are some more pictures of the progress of painting:Good luck to everyone!Roobet username: hZti

comments.body: Congratulations, you are a faithful bounty manager I believe you will soon become popular with everyone. And one thing you will notice now is that a lot of new managers are coming and they are bringing a lot of new projects here. But most projects are scandalous. My point is, you don't have to wait for these scandalous projects like theirs. Your project may be a little less but the project you have come up with should not be as scandalous as everyone else.That's why I like everything about you. Go ahead, love you boss
